overview: Six stunning soldiers are called to action in 3 deliciously dirty duos in Double Time 8!  Diego and Elijah are two of my personal favorites and they rock the bedroom in an awesome duo scene that'll leave you breathless. Both of these guys are all smiles at the thought of getting it on with one another. They've met several times in the past, but they've never done a scene together and I think the tension has been building all this time. Cast: Kaden Saylor,Diego, Dorian, Elijah, Evan, Styx
title: Double Time 8
